{
  "stem": "16571.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 315.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you went in from this room into another room where you was dished out with these white stripes after being shaved and-- your head and your private parts, and all the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but what I did forget to say is our clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said, don't forget what your-- where-- where your clothes will be when you come back for them, and all the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember I had a treasured [? pen, ?] the first time I had a [? pen for ?] Pesach.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was given to me by my sister, who-- was strange, but she was giving it to me before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- so I-- I made sure that I knew exactly where my clothes are going to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I never-- was never taken back to them clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We can never see them again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from there, as I said, we met up-- my brother and my-- my father and myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And slowly, sort of daily they called out different transports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I lost both of them within about a week to 10 days, until I was called and I was taken on this transport to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As-- as we arrived in Buchenwald, again, it was not like before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like [SPEAKING GERMAN], because they had you there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you was-- you had striped clothes, and you had shaved heads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you-- they were not frightened that you're going to run away or disappear or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were just marched into five in a line, and we were marched off to the blocks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I finished up with the rest of them in blocks, they was going right up to about 80.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think I was this time in Block 67.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
